                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-108-18621215 t18621215-108-punishment-2"></join>Ten Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">KNOWLES</hi>.†—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18621215-108-punishment-3" type="punishmentDescription">
